wiki.content: "After LIKE" is a song recorded by South Korean girl group IVE. It was released on August 22, 2022 as the lead single of their third single album of the same name. The track samples Gloria Gaynor’s legendary 1978 hit “I Will Survive,” written by Freddie Perren and Dino Fekaris, who are credited on the track due to the sample. After LIKE was written by Seo Ji-eum, with rap-making by South Korean rapper Mad Clown, under the pseudonym Mommy Son, and member Rei, composed by Ryan Jhun, Anders Nilsen, Andrè Jensen and Iselin Solheim, and arranged by Jhun, Nilsen, Avin and Slay.
